  <h2>Little Eyes International at a glance</h2>
  <p>Little Eyes International is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization based in Arizona.
    As pediatric eye care providers, our goal is to offer optical, clinical, and surgical
    eye care services to underserved children in Arizona and Mexico. Our mission is to prevent
    and cure childhood blindness in patients from all socioeconomic backgrounds.</p>
